1
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Those who ceaselessly hone 
their killing arts are known as "Masters."</i></font>

2
00:00:17,770 --> 00:00:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After many generations, 
they have gained lethal abilities</i></font>

3
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>called "Modified Bloodlines."</i></font>

4
00:00:26,040 --> 00:00:31,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the story of one such Master, 
the Poison Master, Hikaru Gero,</i></font>

5
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:34,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and his attempts to get married.</i></font>

6
00:02:06,470 --> 00:02:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

7
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:17,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, thanks for waiting!</font>

8
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:17,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><b><font color="#f8fbe4">Shinei College Camping Club</font></b></font></font></font>

9
00:02:17,860 --> 00:02:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's your lemon sours.</font>

10
00:02:21,530 --> 00:02:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hope Gero's up to this.</i></font>

11
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:29,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So this is a college welcome party?
 I've heard the legends.</i></font>

12
00:02:31,200 --> 00:02:33,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never thought my job 
would take me to one.</i></font>

13
00:02:33,660 --> 00:02:35,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">New students, gather round.</font>

14
00:02:35,660 --> 00:02:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming.</font>

15
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:44,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. To all of us starting college
 and meeting each other.</font>

16
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:45,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

17
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

18
00:02:52,220 --> 00:02:54,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a first-year, right?</font>

19
00:02:55,660 --> 00:02:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's the party? Having fun?</font>

20
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh... Huh?</font>

21
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:13,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm h-having a blast.</font>

22
00:03:13,780 --> 00:03:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did I do?</font>

23
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever we did, sorry.</font>

24
00:03:16,410 --> 00:03:18,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-See you around.</font>

25
00:03:22,490 --> 00:03:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was my chance to talk 
with older students, and I blew it.</font>

26
00:03:28,810 --> 00:03:33,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hire you as a bodyguard for my niece, 
who starts university this spring.</font>

27
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if possible, without standing out.</font>

28
00:03:40,410 --> 00:03:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Shiori Ureshino.</font>

29
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her father, my older brother, built this company
 from the ground up in one generation,</font>

30
00:03:49,580 --> 00:03:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but illness took him a year ago.</font>

31
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:56,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He left a will stating his daughter, Shiori,</font>

32
00:03:54,050 --> 00:03:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Yeah! You got it!</i></font>

33
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="10">Hold still while balancing a tray!</font></b></font></font>

34
00:03:56,000 --> 00:04:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will succeed him as CEO 
once she comes of age.</font>

35
00:03:56,010 --> 00:03:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Keep going!</i></font>

36
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But someone has other ideas.</font>

37
00:04:06,350 --> 00:04:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My older sister.</font>

38
00:04:08,780 --> 00:04:12,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She claims Balzak is rightfully hers.</font>

39
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14">Second Son
Mitsuhiko</font></font></font>

40
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14">Eldest Daughter
Futae</font></font></font>

41
00:04:10,190 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14">Eldest Son (Deceased)
Kazuhito</font></font></font>

42
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't exactly know what Futae will try,</font>

43
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but rumor has it she's hired someone 
who uses strange techniques</font>

44
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:23,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that no ordinary expert 
has a hope of stopping.</font>

45
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, thank you very much
 for taking this job.</font>

46
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="16"><font color="#685356">Student ID</font></font></b></font></font>

47
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12"><font color="#4b3341">Name:</font></font></b></font></font>

48
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="18"><font color="#4b3341">Daigo Oshima</font></font></b></font></font>

49
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="10"><font color="#4b3341">Date of birth:</font></font></b></font></font>

50
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12"><font color="#4b3341">20**/11/24</font></font></b></font></font>

51
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="10"><font color="#4b3341">Blood type:</font></font></b></font></font>

52
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="10"><font color="#4b3341">Date issued:</font></font></b></font></font>

53
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Georgia"><b><font size="12"><font color="#4b3341">20**/**/**</font></font></b></font></font>

54
00:04:30,120 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="7"><font color="#4b3341">We certify that the above is a student of this university</font></font></b></font></font>

55
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's your student ID.</font>

56
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:36,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starting today, you're Daigo Oshima,
 a third-year student.</font>

57
00:04:36,220 --> 00:04:37,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

58
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Excuse me.</font>

59
00:04:39,750 --> 00:04:46,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know this is, uh, sudden,
but I'd like to, well...</font>

60
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">go to a drinking party.</font>

61
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A party? That's a risk you don't need.</font>

62
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

63
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh, all right.</font>

64
00:05:05,990 --> 00:05:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="20"><b><font color="#f8fbe4">Shinei College Camping Club</font></b></font></font></font>

65
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, next person.</font>

66
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm Shiori Ureshino, 
a first-year economics major.</font>

67
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-And, uh...</font>

68
00:05:25,810 --> 00:05:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I say now?</i></font>

69
00:05:28,170 --> 00:05:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}My favorite games. Where I'm from. A funny joke. Some generational thing.</i></font>

70
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Ria coasts. Aging society. Romantic gossip. A time I messed up. My hobbies.</i></font>

71
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}TV shows. Another failure. Tomorrow's weather. Hot yoga. Macroeconomics.</i></font>

72
00:05:32,020 --> 00:05:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}That café's new item. The Tokugawa Shogunate. Particle physics. Inverted triangle-shaped back.</i></font>

73
00:05:32,390 --> 00:05:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Swahili. Part-time work. Inclined barbell bench press.</i></font>

74
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Dorms. Green iguana. Home run.</i></font>

75
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Welcome party. Aristotle.</i></font>

76
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:47,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Pleased to meet you all.</font>

77
00:05:48,730 --> 00:05:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh, thanks.</font>

78
00:05:52,450 --> 00:05:54,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, next person.</font>

79
00:05:58,760 --> 00:06:00,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you handle a party, Gero?</font>

80
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've gone drinking with 
the Bug Master plenty of times.</font>

81
00:06:04,860 --> 00:06:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm worried. I'd better sneak in.</i></font>

82
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:13,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll show you that a top-notch Master 
is also the life of the party.</i></font>

83
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:17,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daigo Oshima, economics major.</font>

84
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:20,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch as I chug all eight of these.</font>

85
00:06:24,370 --> 00:06:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way that flies these days.</i></font>

86
00:06:31,960 --> 00:06:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This next part is the clincher.</i></font>

87
00:06:41,550 --> 00:06:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we call an ambulance?</font>

88
00:06:58,730 --> 00:07:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That'll get applause for sure.</i></font>

89
00:07:02,270 --> 00:07:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to meet you.</font>

90
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's a water-absorbent polymer.
 Completely harmless.</font>

91
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:10,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a disaster.</i></font>

92
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, who else hasn't 
introduced themselves?</font>

93
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, he's calling you.</font>

94
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="18">Ultimate Relaxation</font></b></font>

95
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="18">Man of the Alps</font></b></font>

96
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b><font size="18">Campfire ASMR</font></b></font>

97
00:07:30,450 --> 00:07:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Naruko.</font>

98
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all.</font>

99
00:07:35,530 --> 00:07:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, what about first name?
 Your major? Stuff like that?</font>

100
00:07:38,730 --> 00:07:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I forget.</font>

101
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What <i>really</i> matters is that I got to meet
 all of you here in this moment.</font>

102
00:07:48,850 --> 00:07:50,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I super thank my lucky stars.</font>

103
00:07:50,990 --> 00:07:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his deal?</font>

104
00:07:52,380 --> 00:07:54,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's been spacing out this whole time.</font>

105
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I super thank them.</font>

106
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He barely said anything.</font>

107
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd he say it twice?</font>

108
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's the one for me.</font>

109
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naruko, is this seat taken?</font>

110
00:08:08,470 --> 00:08:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Mind if I sit here?</font>

111
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wish I got the benefit 
of the doubt like that.</font>

112
00:08:11,290 --> 00:08:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's gotta be his looks.</font>

113
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:17,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drinking parties have hidden depths.</font>

114
00:08:21,390 --> 00:08:23,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, paid by the hour.</font>

115
00:08:24,620 --> 00:08:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, Ureshino.</font>

116
00:08:27,350 --> 00:08:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so sorry.</font>

117
00:08:28,590 --> 00:08:32,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make her cry, Gero. 
Did you take your screwup out on her?</font>

118
00:08:32,330 --> 00:08:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I didn't say anything about that.</font>

119
00:08:37,160 --> 00:08:39,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I mean, why did you
 force yourself to go?</font>

120
00:08:40,290 --> 00:08:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're inheriting a company, so you went
to work on your communication issues.</font>

121
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:46,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get that, but even so...</font>

122
00:08:49,690 --> 00:08:51,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey now.</font>

123
00:08:51,210 --> 00:08:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, Gero?</font>

124
00:08:53,990 --> 00:09:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I'm just so glad you're thinking
 about how I feel.</font>

125
00:09:01,470 --> 00:09:05,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, well, it's not just 
about the company.</font>

126
00:09:05,390 --> 00:09:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to be part of the group.</font>

127
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the very end, my dad said...</font>

128
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:25,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give drinking a try when you turn 20.</font>

129
00:09:29,020 --> 00:09:33,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiori, you're a nice girl,</font>

130
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:36,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but you worry too much 
about what other people think.</font>

131
00:09:36,930 --> 00:09:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Life's more fun when you take 
what's rattling around inside your head</font>

132
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:45,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and bam! You let it all out.</font>

133
00:09:45,680 --> 00:09:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enjoy yourself with people.</font>

134
00:09:50,930 --> 00:09:54,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I want for you.</font>

135
00:10:06,650 --> 00:10:08,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do it.</font>

136
00:10:08,470 --> 00:10:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even here, a flood of words 
sometimes just overwhelms my brain.</font>

137
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ureshino.</font>

138
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:20,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. I just need 
to take the first step.</font>

139
00:10:20,880 --> 00:10:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone will accept me.</font>

140
00:10:24,140 --> 00:10:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brain knows that, 
but I can't help worrying.</font>

141
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if I make people annoyed 
or angry or sad instead?</font>

142
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never even managed to really talk
 to my dad before he...</font>

143
00:10:39,580 --> 00:10:44,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't even get to ask why 
he named me his successor.</font>

144
00:10:46,910 --> 00:10:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

145
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to improve myself.</font>

146
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To get to the point...</font>

147
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where I can laugh away my fear.</font>

148
00:10:58,930 --> 00:11:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You realize someone's 
out to kill you, right?</font>

149
00:11:02,470 --> 00:11:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gero.</font>

150
00:11:05,070 --> 00:11:07,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you've got someplace 
you want to go, I won't stop you.</font>

151
00:11:10,160 --> 00:11:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My job is to keep you safe.</font>

152
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Madam, I have something to report.</font>

153
00:11:21,630 --> 00:11:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her bodyguard is good.</font>

154
00:11:24,280 --> 00:11:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He acts all natural, 
but he leaves no openings.</font>

155
00:11:34,930 --> 00:11:37,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I super forgot to charge it.</font>

156
00:11:40,110 --> 00:11:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="28"><b>The Sound Master</b></font></font></font>

157
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:47,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think this is <i>funny</i>? You've been at this 
for a month and made zero progress.</font>

158
00:11:47,130 --> 00:11:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you realize how much I'm paying you?</font>

159
00:11:49,770 --> 00:11:53,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As if that little girl could run
 a party supplies brand</font>

160
00:11:53,850 --> 00:11:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with a market cap of 1.5 trillion yen.</font>

161
00:11:56,990 --> 00:11:59,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me: When do you plan
 to "dispose" of her?</font>

162
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="20"><b><font color="#100703">3 more days</font></b></font></font></font>

163
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The time is not yet ripe.</font>

164
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:07,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me? Don't give me that crap.</font>

165
00:12:07,920 --> 00:12:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've spent over a month—</font>

166
00:12:17,710 --> 00:12:19,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This bodyguard, Oshima.</font>

167
00:12:19,990 --> 00:12:23,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say he's good, 
but he's still a nobody.</font>

168
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:26,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He won't last a second 
against a Master like you.</font>

169
00:12:26,510 --> 00:12:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Madam, I'm super a man of my word.</font>

170
00:12:30,700 --> 00:12:32,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case...</font>

171
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:35,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either get her to decline the job,</font>

172
00:12:36,210 --> 00:12:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or leave her incapable of taking it.</font>

173
00:12:39,450 --> 00:12:43,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can kill her if that's what it takes.</font>

174
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:52,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gero, you're not a real student. 
Why even bother to listen so attentively?</font>

175
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:55,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all new to me. 
I'm having a great time.</font>

176
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got one hell of a tragic past.</font>

177
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="13"><font color="#ffffff">Economics
\hDepartment</font></font></font></b></font>

178
00:12:58,880 --> 00:13:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="16"><font color="#d27b82">ORIENTATION</font></font></font></b></font>

179
00:12:59,180 --> 00:13:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow.</i></font>

180
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, you there.</font>

181
00:13:02,400 --> 00:13:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Name a product that 
revolutionized its industry.</font>

182
00:13:04,970 --> 00:13:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Uh...</font>

183
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mixy-Mix Max Mix.</font>

184
00:13:08,750 --> 00:13:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only 100 of these legendary kits were made
 for the brand's 30th anniversary.</font>

185
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:17,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, well. You know your stuff.</font>

186
00:13:45,130 --> 00:13:47,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liberating the Mixy-Mix market!</font>

187
00:13:47,410 --> 00:13:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A return to the Mix-aissance!</font>

188
00:13:49,290 --> 00:13:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words, Mixy-Mix...</font>

189
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Max Mix!</font>

190
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:56,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as there are 
passionate students like you,</font>

191
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can make way for 
the next generation without—</font>

192
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It looks like...</i></font>

193
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>since they can't separate me from 
the target, they're using brute force.</i></font>

194
00:14:09,820 --> 00:14:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I don't feel so good.</font>

195
00:14:10,400 --> 00:14:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who here seems suspicious?</i></font>

196
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:16,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone outside?</i></font>

197
00:14:16,830 --> 00:14:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I already checked that 
no one had a line of sight.</i></font>

198
00:14:40,280 --> 00:14:42,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We were attacked all at once.</i></font>

199
00:14:43,050 --> 00:14:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, this is a well-ventilated environment.
 That means it wasn't a gas.</i></font>

200
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In which case...</i></font>

201
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He injected himself with something, 
then sprang into action.</i></font>

202
00:14:56,300 --> 00:15:00,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Were sound waves transmitted remotely
 to shake the room and the people inside?</i></font>

203
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I scrambled his sense of balance, 
and he super recovered in no time.</i></font>

204
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:06,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That should be impossible.</i></font>

205
00:15:06,860 --> 00:15:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one could pull off a precise,
 large-scale attack except...</i></font>

206
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one could whip something 
like that up in an instant except...</i></font>

207
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...a Sound Master.</i></font>

208
00:15:15,710 --> 00:15:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>...a Poison Master.</i></font>

209
00:15:21,500 --> 00:15:22,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gero!</font>

210
00:15:23,450 --> 00:15:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I informed the client.</font>

211
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:30,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Every hitman knows that making it look 
like an accident saves trouble.</font>

212
00:15:30,940 --> 00:15:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ureshino, they planned 
to kill you for sure.</font>

213
00:15:36,190 --> 00:15:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, Gero, should we skip 
the camping trip tomorrow?</font>

214
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an7}<font face="Times New Roman"><font size="7"><font color="#ffffff">Economics
Department</font></font></font></b></font>

215
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial Black"><font size="12"><font color="#995454">ORIENTATION</font></font></font></b></font>

216
00:15:40,070 --> 00:15:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's up to our client.</font>

217
00:15:43,090 --> 00:15:45,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course you can go.</font>

218
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I can?</font>

219
00:15:47,390 --> 00:15:51,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been looking forward 
to this trip for ages.</font>

220
00:15:51,470 --> 00:15:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font size="14"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#c15452">Shiratori</font></b></font></font></font>

221
00:15:52,090 --> 00:15:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no substitute for friends
 you make at school.</font>

222
00:15:56,470 --> 00:15:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So go make lots of them.</font>

223
00:15:58,630 --> 00:16:02,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With those two around, 
you have nothing to worry about.</font>

224
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

225
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:08,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you, Uncle Mitsuhiko.</font>

226
00:16:08,680 --> 00:16:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for keeping you waiting.</font>

227
00:16:10,920 --> 00:16:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no problem. That's a huge bag,
 though. What's in it?</font>

228
00:16:15,650 --> 00:16:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A collapsible umbrella, and uh...
 The rest is secret.</font>

229
00:16:16,960 --> 00:16:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a safe trip.</font>

230
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:28,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We can't guarantee her safety 
even if she stays home.</i></font>

231
00:16:29,450 --> 00:16:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The only way to resolve this
 is to face the enemy.</i></font>

232
00:16:33,950 --> 00:16:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And unlike with Himekawa, we don't know 
when the Sound Master will strike.</i></font>

233
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:42,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is the plan to settle things
 on this trip?</i></font>

234
00:16:48,190 --> 00:16:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, what's this?</font>

235
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:51,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black"><font size="32"><b><font color="#100703">1 more day</font></b></font></font></font>

236
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:53,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A super important promise.</font>

237
00:16:53,550 --> 00:16:55,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such a great guy, Naruko.</font>

238
00:16:55,160 --> 00:16:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make a promise, too.</font>

239
00:16:57,250 --> 00:17:00,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Then, make a promise with me, too.</font>

240
00:17:00,330 --> 00:17:02,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What? No fair.</font>

241
00:17:01,290 --> 00:17:03,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Super important.</font>

242
00:17:21,260 --> 00:17:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A man who can cook attracts triple
 the ladies (Kinosaki approved).</font>

243
00:17:29,880 --> 00:17:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll show you I can cook 
with the best of them.</i></font>

244
00:17:33,190 --> 00:17:37,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, would you like some yakisoba?</font>

245
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would anyone, uh, like some yakisoba?</font>

246
00:17:43,690 --> 00:17:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yakisoba?</font>

247
00:17:46,970 --> 00:17:48,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kinosaki.</font>

248
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:50,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Don't worry about me."</font>

249
00:17:51,810 --> 00:17:54,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what Ureshino told us, remember?</font>

250
00:17:55,190 --> 00:17:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She wants to "figure it out" for herself.</font>

251
00:18:03,410 --> 00:18:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How do I become part of the group?</i></font>

252
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Yakisoba. Sauce. Noodles. Flour. Red pickled ginger.</i></font>

253
00:18:05,610 --> 00:18:09,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Cabbage. Adding water. Throwaway chopsticks. White birch.</i></font>

254
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:09,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Tapioca. 100 yen each. Dance practice.</i></font>

255
00:18:06,980 --> 00:18:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Club activities. Fjords. Transporting flamingos.</i></font>

256
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Water-absorbent polymer. Wild chihuahuas. Rice-field property law.</i></font>

257
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an1}Plate tectonics. Adam Smith. Fortune telling.</i></font>

258
00:18:17,510 --> 00:18:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is she okay?</font>

259
00:18:23,580 --> 00:18:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If talking to people doesn't work...</i></font>

260
00:18:26,450 --> 00:18:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll try something else.</i></font>

261
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with the magical girl getup?</font>

262
00:18:37,330 --> 00:18:39,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing up my sleeves.</font>

263
00:18:40,350 --> 00:18:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's this?</font>

264
00:18:40,490 --> 00:18:41,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And here goes nothing.</font>

265
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}A magic trick?</font>

266
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pan-puru pin-puru pom-po-pun.</font>

267
00:18:45,090 --> 00:18:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pin-puru pan-puru pom-po-pun.</font>

268
00:18:47,950 --> 00:18:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

269
00:18:54,060 --> 00:18:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For my next trick, an extra big helping.</font>

270
00:18:56,590 --> 00:18:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pin-puru pan-puru pom-po-pun!</font>

271
00:18:59,650 --> 00:19:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

272
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You okay?</font>

273
00:19:09,250 --> 00:19:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those were some cool 
magic tricks, Ureshino.</font>

274
00:19:12,670 --> 00:19:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got them from my family's business.</font>

275
00:19:16,140 --> 00:19:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never done that in front of people 
before, and I messed up the finale.</font>

276
00:19:21,670 --> 00:19:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not good with words...</font>

277
00:19:25,500 --> 00:19:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I remembered the performance 
Mr. Gero put on at the party,</font>

278
00:19:30,730 --> 00:19:32,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I thought "That's it!"</font>

279
00:19:34,390 --> 00:19:35,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

280
00:19:40,090 --> 00:19:41,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't really, um...</font>

281
00:19:41,570 --> 00:19:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hmm? What was that?</font>

282
00:19:43,390 --> 00:19:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean...</font>

283
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:47,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're welcome.</font>

284
00:19:48,310 --> 00:19:50,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That reminds me. Have you all heard...</font>

285
00:19:51,690 --> 00:19:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">about the curse of Lord Chladni?</font>

286
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's that?</font>

287
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This used to be a village.</font>

288
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The locals made "offerings" to 
the local deity right up until World War II.</font>

289
00:20:04,210 --> 00:20:07,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once every two years, 
when the crops failed,</font>

290
00:20:07,570 --> 00:20:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">they would pick out 
the youngest child in the village,</font>

291
00:20:12,890 --> 00:20:17,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and lock the child up 
in that shrine there.</font>

292
00:20:42,080 --> 00:20:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They abandoned the custom after the war,</font>

293
00:20:45,430 --> 00:20:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="18"><font color="#433c30">Another Fire: Suspected Arson Continues</font></font></b></font></font>

294
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but landslides, fires, and a bunch
 of other disasters followed.</font>

295
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And although nearly a thousand people
 lived here at its peak,</font>

296
00:20:52,690 --> 00:20:55,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it wasn't long before not a soul remained.</font>

297
00:20:58,130 --> 00:21:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But even now, Lord Chladni 
waits for his next offering.</font>

298
00:21:03,930 --> 00:21:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that is...</font>

299
00:21:05,820 --> 00:21:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you!</font>

300
00:21:08,220 --> 00:21:09,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He made all that up.</font>

301
00:21:09,550 --> 00:21:13,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oshima, no one likes a spoilsport.</font>

302
00:21:13,860 --> 00:21:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Ureshino. It's all true.</font>

303
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's enough buildup.</font>

304
00:21:20,190 --> 00:21:20,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

305
00:21:22,010 --> 00:21:24,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's get this party started.</font>

306
00:21:24,590 --> 00:21:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the moment you've all been 
waiting for: the test of courage.</font>

307
00:21:27,420 --> 00:21:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, for real?</font>

308
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, come on.</font>

309
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, have you seen Naruko?</font>

310
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:34,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd love to pair up with him.</font>

311
00:21:56,480 --> 00:22:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The melody of this forest
is super perfect.</font>

312
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shiori Ureshino.</font>

313
00:22:05,530 --> 00:22:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My killer session with your screams...</font>

314
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...begins now.</font>

315
00:22:27,830 --> 00:22:33,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font size="14"><font face="Georgia">Translator: William Varteresian
Timer: Andy Ellis
Editor: SMR
Quality Control: Salem Alabanza
Final Quality Control: Michelle Tymon</font></font></font>

316
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Escape is super impossible.</font>

317
00:23:47,150 --> 00:23:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is—</font>

318
00:23:47,530 --> 00:23:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#060606">Why the ears?!
Why carry her like that?!</font></b></font></font></font>

319
00:23:47,530 --> 00:23:48,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font size="30"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#060606">Why the ears?!
Why carry her like that?!</font></b></font></font></font>

320
00:23:48,670 --> 00:23:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I've never been in better condition.</font>

321
00:23:48,870 --> 00:23:50,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on tight!</font>

322
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've gotta seize
 this opportunity.</font>

323
00:23:51,380 --> 00:23:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'll super enjoy this.</font>

324
00:23:51,950 --> 00:23:53,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's water-absorbent polymers.</font>

325
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:56,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Georgia"><font size="26"><b>Lord Chladni</b></font></font></font>

326
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: "Lord Chladni."</font>

